sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 👤 Пользователь
    participant FE as Frontend (SPA)
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Cart as Cart Service
    participant Inv as Inventory Service
    participant Prof as User Profile Service
    participant Ord as Order Service
    participant Pay as Payment Service
    participant PGW as Payment Gateway
    participant Bank as 🏦 Банк
    participant Kafka as 📨 Event Bus
    participant Notif as Notification Service

    User->>FE: Нажать "Оформить заказ"
    FE->>GW: POST /checkout (JWT)
    GW->>Cart: GetCart(cartId)
    Cart-->>GW: CartSnapshot
    GW->>Prof: GetUserDefaults(userId)
    Prof-->>GW: Address + PaymentMethod
    GW-->>FE: CheckoutData (prefilled)
    FE-->>User: Показать форму checkout

    User->>FE: Подтвердить заказ
    FE->>GW: POST /orders (cartSnapshot + deliveryData)
    GW->>Inv: ReserveItem(bookId, qty=1)
    Inv-->>GW: ReservationID (TTL=30min)
    GW->>Ord: CreateOrder(...)
    Ord-->>GW: OrderID, Status=CONFIRMED
    Ord->>Kafka: Publish order.created

    GW->>Pay: InitiatePayment(orderId, amount)
    Pay->>PGW: POST /payment-intents (token, amount, idempotency_key)
    PGW-->>Pay: payment_intent_id, status=processing

    alt 3DS Required
        PGW-->>FE: Redirect to 3DS
        FE-->>User: 3DS-окно банка
        User->>Bank: Подтвердить платёж
        Bank-->>PGW: 3DS Success
    end

    PGW->>Bank: Authorize transaction
    Bank-->>PGW: Authorization code

    PGW->>Pay: WEBHOOK payment_intent.succeeded
    Pay->>Kafka: Publish payment.succeeded

    Kafka->>Ord: Event: payment.succeeded
    Ord->>Ord: Update Status → PAID

    Kafka->>Notif: Event: payment.succeeded
    Notif->>User: 📧 Email-квитанция

    Ord-->>FE: Order confirmed
    FE-->>User: ✅ Экран подтверждения
